honored Lemire=E2=80=99s petition to work more hospitable hours, recognizin=
g his past sacrifice hosting a 5 a.m. show, and found a way to make it work=
=2E Alas, there=E2=80=99s no such flexi=
bility anymore. <br/><br/>It=E2=80=99s=
 exactly these kinds of diminished expectations that have talent and their =
agents in such a funk. And it may also explain why there=E2=80=99s been so =
